ds and the world with the highest score on the Leaderboard.\n\nArcade Series Motobike Racing has all the fun and excitement of an Arcade game on your console. Stack your quarters relive the classic game play.", "short_description": "SGN brings the Arcade home with Arcade Series Motobike Racing.  Arcade style Motorbike racing on your VR Headset! \n\nArcade Series Motobike Racing has all the fun and excitement of an Arcade game on your console. Stack your quarters relive the classic game play."}]}, "developer_name": "Star Gaming Network", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sgngames.com/privacypolicy.php", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://sgngames.com/termsofservice.php", "publisher_name": "Star Gaming Network", "support_website_url": "http://sgngames.com/contactus.php", "website_url": "http://sgngames.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "RACING"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "737606360547229"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "2636774309772335", "version": "1.0"}, "id": "457727881564345", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2616254075157692", "is_conce